Almanac: Mai Gyara Geiger
Yanzu ga wani shafi daga cikin mujallarmu ta "Sunday Morning" mai suna Almanac: 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekara 136 da ta shige, da kuma RATAU ... ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyya Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a ƙasar Jamus.
Geiger ya ƙirƙiri hanyar sanin radiation da kuma auna shi, kuma hakan ya sa aka ƙirƙiri wani na'ura mai suna Geiger Counter.
A matsayin tushen ci gaban kimiyya tun lokacin da aka kafa shi, Geiger Counter ya zama tushen al'adu, kamar yadda a cikin wasan kwaikwayo na 1950 na "Bells of Coronado", wanda ya ƙunshi wasu masu fasaha na kimiyya da suka hada da Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutumin: "To, menene gaskiya?"
Rogers: "Wannan shi ne Geiger Counter, wanda ake amfani da shi wajen auna yawan rediyo a wasu duwatsu, kamar su uranium.
Idan ka saka waɗannan na'urorin a kunnuwanka, za ka iya jin ƙarfin da ake samu daga cikin radiation da ke cikin dutsen".
Evans: "To, ka ce an yi shi!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, kwanaki kaɗan kafin ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
Amma har yanzu akwai wani kayan aiki da ake kira da sunansa.
