Kit Harington, mai wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones, ya yi fushi da mutanen da suke da irin wannan halin
Kit Harington ya shahara sosai a wasan kwaikwayon da ya yi na Jon Snow a wasan kwaikwayo na HBO na Game of Thrones.
Amma wannan jarumi mai ƙarfi mai ƙarfi 31, ya yi fushi sosai da macho hero mai ƙyama, yana cewa wannan fim ɗin yana nufin cewa dole ne yara maza su kasance masu ƙwazo don su sami daraja.
A cikin jawabinsa ga jaridar Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya yi tunanin cewa akwai wani abu da ba daidai ba kuma yana son sanin yadda za a magance wannan halin cin zarafin mata a wannan lokacin #MeToo.
Kit, mai shekara 31, wadda ta auri Rose Leslie, mai yin fim din Game of Thrones, ta ce ta ji cewa 'ta yi aiki tuƙuru' don ta magance wannan matsalar.
Ya ce: 'Ina jin kaina, ina bukatar in yi aiki tuƙuru, a yanzu - ina neman gafara game da abin da muka yi a matsayinmu na maza?
'Me za mu koya wa maza da suka manyanta, saboda matsalolin da muke fuskanta a yau?'
Kit ya ce rediyon ya jawo matsalar da ake yi wa maza da yawa domin yawan nuna nuna ƙarfi.
Ya ci gaba da cewa: 'Me muka haifa da shi kuma menene muka koya?
Shin ana koyar da su a talabijin ko kuma a kan titi don su sa samari su ji cewa suna bukatar su zama maza?
Ina ganin wannan yana ɗaya daga cikin tambayoyin da suka fi muhimmanci a zamaninmu - za mu iya canja wannan halin?
Gama akwai wani abu da bai dace ba a kan waɗannan yara.
A wannan tattaunawar kuma ya amince cewa ba zai ci gaba da yin wani shiri na sake buga ko kuma na musamman na Game of Thrones ba sa'ad da aka kammala shirin a lokacin bazara mai zuwa, kuma ya ce na daina yin wasan kwaikwayo da kuma yin faɗa da doki'.
Daga watan Nuwamba Kit zai halarci wasan kwaikwayo na Sam Shepard mai suna True West wanda ya ƙunshi mai wasan kwaikwayo da ɗan'uwansa mai lalata.
Wannan ɗan wasan ya bayyana cewa yana ganin cewa saduwa da matarsa, Rose, ita ce mafi kyawun abin da ya faru a cikin wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones.
Ya ce, 'Ta wurin wannan, na riƙe matata, kuma ta haka ne ta sa ni in sami rai a nan gaba, da kuma iyalina.'
Rose ta yi wa Ygritte, ƙaunatacciyar mai kula da Kit mai suna Jon Snow, rawa a wasan kwaikwayon da ya zama sananne a wasan kwaikwayon Emmy.
