Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa jawabin da ta fito na sanatan GOP' ya yada 'ƙaryace-ƙaryace masu haɗari' da kuma 'tunanin da ba su dace ba'
A ranar Asabar, Rep. Maxine Waters ta yi watsi da zargin cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya wallafa bayanan 'yan majalisar Republican guda uku a shafukan Wikipedia na wannan kundin.
Wannan dan Democrat na Los Angeles ya ce "masu goyon baya na dama" ne suka yi wannan tunanin, wato, masu wallafa siyasa da kuma shafukan yanar gizo.
Waters ya rubuta a shafinsa na Twitter cewa: "Ƙarya, ƙarya, ƙarya mai zurfi".
An ba da rahoton cewa an yi amfani da wayar tarho da kuma wayar tarho a cikin wani labari da aka yi wa jama'a.
Wani mutum da ba a san shi ba ne ya wallafa wannan labarin a dandalin Intane a ranar Alhamis, a lokacin da ake sauraron majalisar dattawa game da zargin da ake yi game da laifin da aka yi wa Brett Kavanaugh da aka zaɓa a kotun koli.
Bayan da sanatoci uku suka kammala shari'ar Kavanaugh, sai labarin ya bazu.
Shafukan yanar gizo na Conservative kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ce ofishin Waters ne ya yi amfani da adireshin IP don gano mai aikawa kuma ya yi amfani da shi wajen yada labarin wani ma'aikacin Waters, in ji takardar Hill.
"Wannan ra'ayin da ba a tabbatar da shi ba ƙarya ce mai tsanani da kuma ban tsoro", in ji Waters.
"Bawana, wanda ka sanar da mu'ujizai da kuma maganganun da kake yi, da kuma ƙwarewar da kake yi ta wurin wannan mugun ruɗi da kuma ƙarya, ba ya faɗa wannan.
"Wannan mutumin yana da mummunan tunani kuma yana da ban tsoro.
Wannan bayanin da Waters ya yi ya yi tasiri sosai a kan dandalin sada zumunta, har da mai ba da rahoto na fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙin yarda ya sa ni fushi", in ji Fleischer.
"Wannan yana nufin cewa ba shi da zuciya ta zama mamba na Ƙungiyar Shari'a.
Idan aka yi wa mutum horo, kada ya yi fushi.
Bai kamata ya yi fushi don ya kāre kansa ba.
Bai kamata ya yi tambaya ba game da dalilin da ya sa mai zargin ya tsaya.
Amma ya kamata ya zama mai tawali'u da kuma haƙuri".
Fleischer ya yi ƙoƙari ya yi koyi da fushin Waters da na 'yan Democrat da ya nuna cewa ya yi fushi da Alkali Kavanaugh, wanda masu tuhumarsa suka zarge shi da fushin da ya yi a lokacin da ake sauraron shari'ar ranar Talata.
Omar Navarro, wanda ya tsaya a takarar Republican don kawar da Waters a zaben tsakiyar kakar, ya yi tsokaci a shafinsa na Twitter.
"Wannan ya fi girma idan gaskiya ne", in ji ta a shafin Twitter.
A cikin jawabinsa, Waters ya ce ofishinsa ya yi wa "masu da'awar da suka shafi wannan lamarin da kuma wadanda ke aiki da hukumar tsaro game da wannan zargin.
Sun ce: "Za mu tabbatar da cewa an gano masu aikata laifi, kuma za mu tabbatar da cewa za a hukunta su don ayyukansu na lalata da kuma haɗari ga kowa da kuma ma'aikatansa".
Johnny English Ya Sake Sake Sakewa - Wani Fuskar Rowan Atkinson
Yanzu ya zama al'ada a yi watsi da Brexit a duk wani sabon tsarin da ya shafi tarihin Birtaniya da kuma abin da ke faruwa da wannan sabon tsarin wasan kwaikwayo mai ban sha'awa da ake kira Johnny English action-comedy spoof franchise - wanda Johnny English ya fara a shekara ta 2003 kuma ya sake dawowa a shekara ta 2011 a matsayin Johnny English Reborn.
Zai iya kawo wani abin dariya game da matsalarmu a matsayinmu na duniya da kuma game da gatan da muke da shi na tura kayayyakinmu zuwa ƙasashen waje?
A kowane hali, Johnny English mai idanu masu kyau, fuskarsa mai ban mamaki ta sake buɗewa a karo na biyu don yin wasan kwaikwayo - suna da ya nuna cewa shi ne mafi girman mai wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo na ƙasar waje.
Wani mutum yana amfani da wauta mai ban dariya da yawa don haɗawa da wasan kwaikwayo kamar ƙaramin Mai bincike, yana kwaikwayon Mr Bean a cikin wani nau'i na musamman kamar wanda ya ƙara murya zuwa waƙar Chariots of Fire a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta London 2012.
Da farko, ya dogara ne ga Atkinson, wani ɗan ƙasa mai ƙwazo da kuma ƙwararren masani wanda yake cikin ƙungiyar da ake kira Barclaycard TV, wadda ta hana shi yin duk wani abin da zai iya sa ya yi rashin lafiya.
Akwai abu ɗaya ko biyu masu kyau a cikin sabon tsarin tsarin JE.
Na yi farin ciki sosai da na ga Johnny English yana tafiya zuwa jirgin sama da rigar soja da kuma fuka - fukan jirgin sama da ke ɗauke da shi a kan ƙafarsa.
Kyautar Atkinson ta zama abin ban dariya, amma wani lokacin ban dariya yana da ɗan gajeren lokaci fiye da yadda ake tsammani, musamman ma lokacin da wasan kwaikwayo magani kamar 007 da Mission Impossible suka kasance yanzu ban dariya a matsayin ingantawa
Alamu na nishaɗi na gaskiya sun fi na manya kyau, kuma a yawancin abubuwan da Johnny English ya yi ba su da wani irin nishaɗi mai kyau kamar abin da ya faru a wasan Atkinson a matsayin Bean.
Labarin da ake yi a wannan shekara shi ne cewa ƙasar Britaniya tana cikin mawuyacin hali.
Wani ɗan fashin kan layi ya shiga cikin hanyar sadarwa ta yanar gizo mai zurfi ta 'yan sandan Burtaniya, yana bayyana gaskiyar duk wakilan Burtaniya da ke aiki, abin da ya ba da mamaki ga wani da ke aiki a lokacin - aikin da Kevin Eldon bai yi ba.
Wannan abu ne mai wuya ga firaministan da ke da girman kai da kuma rashin ƙarfi, wanda ke fama da rashin ikon shugabancinsa da kuma sanannun sanannun siyasa: Emma Thompson ta yi nasara wajen taka rawa a matsayin quasi-Teresa-May amma ba ta da yawa a cikin tsarin kalmomin da za a yi amfani da su.
Sai aka ce wa ma'aikatan da suka yi aiki a wurin su ba da duk wani aiki da aka yi da su, su mayar da duk wanda ya yi aiki a wurin.
Wannan ya ƙunshi Johnny English, wanda yanzu shi ne shugaban makarantar, amma yana ba da wasu shawarwari masu ban sha'awa game da yin aiki a ɓoye: wani abin ban dariya, lokacin da English yake koyar da darussan wasan kwaikwayo a Makarantar Rock.
