Wani wakilin Amirka ya yi zargin cewa kasar Sin tana "taurin kai" ta wajen " yada matsala"
Ba da daɗewa ba bayan da wata jarida ta kasar Sin ta wallafa wani labari a kan shafin Amurka game da amfanin da ke tattare da cinikayya tsakanin Amirka da China, wani ofishin jakadancin Amirka a kasar Sin ya bukaci birnin Beijing ya yi amfani da jaridar Amirka don ya ba da labari mai wuya.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya ba da rahoto a cikin jaridar China Daily da kuma wani shafi na Des Moines Register - wata takarda da ta fi kowa daraja a Iowa - a ranar Laraba bayan da ya yi kira ga kasar Sin ta shiga cikin zaben majalisar dokokin Amirka na ranar 6 ga Nuwamba, wanda kasar ta ƙi.
Shugaban Trump ya yi ikirarin cewa Beijing na kokarin shiga zaben Amurka ne, inda ya tabbatar da cewa wasu jami'an Amurka sun bayyana wa Reuters cewa Washington na shirin amfani da wani sabon tsari don kawo matsala ga kasar Sin.
Duk da cewa ana iya samun sanarwa a cikin jaridu a ƙasashe da yawa, Beijing da Washington suna cikin mawuyacin rikici na kasuwanci da ya sa harajin shigo da kayayyaki ya ƙaru.
An yi amfani da harajin da aka yi wa kasar Sin a farkon shekara don ya shafi masu sayar da kayayyaki a biranen da suka fi so a matsayin masu goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, kamar yadda masu lura da harkokin kasuwanci a kasar Sin suka ce.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin da ya yi aiki na dogon lokaci a matsayin Gwamna na Iowa, ya ce Beijing ta yi wa 'yan kasuwa da manoma da kuma 'yan kasuwa na Amirka laifi.
Branstad ya rubuta a cikin wani rahoto a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register na Lahadi cewa: "China tana ƙara matsa lamba ta wajen yin amfani da mujallu masu ƙalubale don yin kasuwanci".
Branstad ya rubuta: "Ta hanyar yin amfani da wannan babbar hanyar kasuwanci, gwamnatin Sin tana nuna wa 'yancin Amirka da kuma 'yancin yin magana a kan takardar kuɗi a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A wani ɓangare kuma, a kan teburin wata hanya a birnin Beijing, ba za ka ga wani abu da ya saɓa wa abin da jama'ar Sin suke faɗa game da burin da suke fuskanta na cinikayya da ke raguwa ba, wato, cewa Jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta Sin ta rufe tashoshin sadarwa a kasar", in ji su.
