An ajiye Mickelson a ranar Asabar saboda rashin nasarar da ya samu a gasar Ryder Cup
A ranar Lahadi, dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai yi wasan Ryder Cup karo na 47 a duniya, amma zai yi aiki tuƙuru don ya guji lokacin da ya fi ƙarfinsa.
