An shirya a soma amfani da sabon jirgin ruwan jirgin ruwa na rundunar sojan ruwa na Jamus a shekara ta 2014 don maye gurbin tsohon jirgin ruwan Cold War, amma ba a yi amfani da shi ba har zuwa wannan shekarar, saboda rashin kayan aiki da kuma farashin kayayyaki.
