Girgizar ƙasa da ambaliyar ruwa a ƙasar Indonesia
A ranar Talata, mutane ɗari uku da huɗu suka mutu a girgizar ƙasa da ambaliyar ruwa da ta faru a birnin Palos, bisa ga rahoton dattawa.
A lokacin da ake ci gaba da yin hakan, ba a samun rahoto daga yankin Donggala, da ke arewacin Palu, inda ake samun girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5.
A birnin Palus, an bincika mutane wajen 16,000 a lokacin da aka yi wannan hatsarin.
Ga wasu bayanai game da yankin Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu ita ce babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, kuma a shekara ta 2017 yawan mutanen yankin ya kai 379,800.
A lokacin da aka yi girgizar ƙasa da ambaliyar ruwa, birnin ya yi bikin cika shekara 40 da samun 'yancin kai.
Donggala wani yanki ne mai nisan kilomita 300 (180 mil) na gabashin Sulawesi.
A shekara ta 2017, yawan mutanen da ke wannan yankin ya kai 299,200.
Fishing da kuma noma su ne manyan ayyukan da ke samar da tattalin arziki a lardin Central Sulawesi, musamman a yankin Donggala.
Ana samun ƙarfe mai yawa a wannan lardin, amma mafi yawan ƙarfe a Morowali, a Sulawesi.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, girgizar ƙasa da ambaliyar ruwa sun sha birnin Palu da kuma Donggala sau da yawa, in ji Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, ambaliyar ruwa ta kashe mutane 200 kuma ta lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a birnin Donggala.
A shekara ta 1996, raƙuman ruwa sun kai ga birnin Donggala, inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Kasar Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake kira Pacific Ring of Fire kuma tana fama da girgizar ƙasa sau da yawa.
Wannan jerin sunayen girgizar ƙasa da ambaliyar ruwa mafi girma a cikin shekaru da suka wuce:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa ta afku a lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra kuma ta jawo ambaliyar ruwa a ƙasashe 14, ta kashe mutane 226,000 a tekun Tekun Indiya, da yawa daga cikinsu sun mutu a yankin Aceh.
2005: An yi wani babban taro a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen watan Oktoba da kuma farkon watan Shinde.
Dubban mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa yankin Java, mafi yawan mutane a Indonesia, kuma ta jawo raƙuman ruwa a gabar kudu, inda kusan mutane 700 suka mutu.
A shekara ta 2009: Girgizar ƙasa ta yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi 7.6 a birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
An kashe mutane wajen 1,100.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afka wa wani tsibiri a tsibirin Mentawai kusa da Sumatra, kuma ta jawo raƙuman ruwa mai tsawon mita 10 da suka halaka birane da yawa kuma suka kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani ƙaramin girgizar ƙasa ya afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, kuma hakan ya jawo damuwa da kuma lalacewa a lokacin da aka tuna da girgizar ƙasa da ambaliyar ruwa da aka yi a shekara ta 2004.
Babu ambaliyar ruwa a wannan lokacin, amma fiye da mutane 100 sun mutu a sakamakon ambaliyar.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani ta yi ta a Lombok, babban birni na yawon buɗe ido a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, yawancinsu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasa ta lalata gine -gine da yawa kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon buɗe ido ba su da gida.
