'Yan kotun New York suna neman a yanke hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda aka yi niyyar kai hari a birnin New York inda aka kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taɓa yi a ƙasar ba a kan wani abu da ya shafi ƙasar tun 1953.
An yi zargin cewa Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi amfani da motar Home Depot wajen yin hatsarin a kan titin da ke kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, yana bin wasu masu tafiya a kan kekuna a lokacin bazara.
Don a yi masa hukuncin kisa, kotun dole ne ta tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas "a fili" kuma ya yi masa rauni "a fili", in ji sanarwar da aka yi a Kotu ta Kudu ta New York.
Dukansu suna da hukuncin kisa bisa ga takardar kotu.
Bayan makonni da suka wuce, sai wani kotu ta yanke hukuncin kisa a kan Saipov da laifuffuka 22, ciki har da kisa takwas da ake tuhuma da su da laifin yin lalata da mutane, wanda ake amfani da shi a matsayin lauya a shari'ar da ba ta da laifi, da kuma laifin lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce wannan harin ya bukaci "shirya da kuma shiri", suna kwatanta Saipov da "matsananci, rashin tausayi, da kuma rashin tausayi".
"Saipov ya jawo wa danginsa da abokansa rauni, fushi, da kuma rashi, kamar Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da kuma Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", in ji sanarwar.
