A shekara ta 1953, an yi wa gwamnatin New York hukuncin kisa na ƙarshe a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, maza da mata da aka yanke musu hukuncin kisa a kan laifin yin leƙen asiri a lokacin Sojan Soviet a shekara biyu da ta shige.
